title: Microsoft Office ProPlus 2013 SP1 VL x64 en-US November 2015
description:
************************************************************
Microsoft Office ProPlus 2013 SP1 VL x64 en-US November 2015 
************************************************************

System requirements
-------------------

Windows 10/8.1/8,7 SP1 + Server/Server 2012 R2/2012/Server 2008 R2 (64-bit)

Release Info
------------

- Language: en-US
- Channel: Volume License
- Version: 15.0.4763.1000
- Format: DAA (ISO compressed)

Integrated updates 10/11/2015
-----------------------------

Definition Update for Microsoft Office 2013 (KB3101493)
Security Update for Microsoft Access 2013 (KB3085584)
Security Update for Microsoft Excel 2013 (KB3101499)
Security Update for Microsoft InfoPath 2013 (KB3054793)
Security Update for Microsoft Office 2013 (KB3085572)

Update for Microsoft Office 2013 (KB3101374)

Update for Microsoft Office 2013 (KB3101501)
Update for Microsoft OneDrive for Business (KB3101505)
Update for Microsoft Outlook 2013 (KB3101488)
Update for SharePoint Designer 2013 (KB3101366)

Installation
------------

Extract ZIP archive
If you have PowerIso installed, just convert DAA file to ISO format
If you don't: run the batch file Makeiso (this will convert the DAA file to ISO)

- Mount or burn ISO file and install Office
- Install Visual Studio for Office Runtime from add-ins folder (required update)
- Activate using Microsoft Toolkit 2.5.3 (in add-ins folder, click the Office button, install AutoKMS, and click the Activate button)

Bonus (Add-ins folder)
----------------------

- Classic Menu for Office v5.85 + serial
- Office Tab v9.81 + serial
- Merge Remove Sign In icon Office 2013 reg file to remove the "Sign in" option

Please SEED for a while!
